#: ../../../appendix/api-quick-reference.md:54
msgid ""
"Use these annotations only on an explicit counted `while` loop inside a "
"`#[kernel]` or `#[device]` function. Range-based `for` loops are not yet "
"recognized by the unroll pass. Nested loops and multiple `continue` paths "
"are supported. Full `#[unroll]` preserves `break` paths and multiple exit "
"targets."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../appendix/api-quick-reference.md:59
msgid ""
"Partial `#[unroll(N)]` requires a positive step, a `<` or `<=` test, an "
"unchanging limit, and no exit besides the normal header test. Other requests "
"warn and are not unrolled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../appendix/api-quick-reference.md:63
msgid ""
"One annotation may create at most 1,024 body copies, 8,192 cloned basic "
"blocks, and 65,536 cloned operations. Larger requests warn and are not "
"unrolled."
msgstr ""

